data.description: Adorable Florida cottage available in Santa Rosa Beach!! New Metal Roof in 2022! New Water Heater in 2022! New Ac in 2018! New Fencing in 2023! New Interior/Exterior Paint in 2023! Florida room added in 2019! Plenty of room for your boat or RV!! This home has been very well maintained by the current owners and shows pride in ownership though out. The living room, kitchen, and dining area are all open concept, with tile floors throughout these main areas. The 9ft ceilings, crown molding and neutral paint colors create a wide open and relaxing space for you to spend time with friends or family! The kitchen offers granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and kitchen island, with plenty of room for the chef of the house to stretch out. The bedrooms are set up very well with a recent upgrade to create a 2nd master with en suite bathroom. Bathrooms have been updated to include quartz countertops, walk-in showers and glass shower door. The porches of this house are fantastic, with a large front porch with wooden interlocking floor tiles. The back porch has been extended and screened in for protection from the bugs and elements, creating a 15'x30' Florida room for your serene outdoor living space! The back yard was recently fenced in for your pets and/or children's enjoyment! The entire exterior and interior of this home has just been freshly repainted this year! This home offers all the finished updates and upgrades making it move-in ready for your family! Not only that, the location couldn't be better, the home is less than 5 minutes from Cessna Landing public park and boat launch, and just 10 minutes to 30A, Gulf Place shops, and Ed Walline public beach access to the beautiful Beaches of South Walton! It is also central to all that Santa Rosa Beach has to offer, including shopping, dining, and medical offices. Call me today to discuss and schedule a private tour!
